item.title: Contact form
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[text* name class:left-input-box class:form-control placeholder "Name"]
[email* email class:left-input-box class:form-control placeholder "Email"]

[submit id:button-input-send class:btn class:btn-primary class:btn-lg class:btn-block "Send Message"]
